  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline at sunset or sunrise, dominated by a vibrant and dramatic sky. The sky is layered with dense, textured clouds, transitioning from a fiery orange near the horizon to deep purples and grays higher up. A distant cityscape is silhouetted against the bright light, revealing a mix of buildings and infrastructure. A body of water, possibly a bay or ocean, stretches out before the city, reflecting the colors of the sky.  In the foreground, the image is framed by dark, dense foliage of trees and shrubs, creating a sense of depth and a natural border.  A few scattered lights illuminate the city below, suggesting the presence of life and activity. The overall composition is expansive and captures a stunning moment of natural beauty and urban landscape.",
